ern to a recursive classpath directory pattern; adjust the test logic to assert the Spring 7 hint shape.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"If the generated test expands into MockMvc or servlet-specific APIs, it may then need web/servlet test dependencies, but the current failing AOT TestContext path does not.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_078f5813c88570e3016a28587574588190b219b207c17f650f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1629, "output": 1005, "cacheRead": 37888, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 40522, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781028960735, "responseId": "resp_078f5813c88570e3016a2858615c148190bdce0a8395b9292f"}}
